 would get the 2 gold and whatever type donations, but then sometimes someone would come up and tell ya they really appreciated the way you handled that and hand ya something big (at level 14 i got a 50pp donation once WOW, and another time I got a full backpack of fine steel weapons--Thanks Sean hehe).<br>
<br>
Anyhow, as for cash, everyone that is an actual new character at that level that does not have higher level friends that twink them and whatnot, goes through the same cashflow problems you do. Good luck to you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
